Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a swarm of robots and their coordination to solve a gathering problem. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also a likely category as the paper deals with the movement and coordination of robots. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with distributed algorithms executed by every robot. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper proposes an algorithm for solving the gathering problem. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with the control and coordination of a swarm of robots.
